BI) at Cambridge...”</span><span style="color:#333333; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">Food and Water Watch</span></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><a href="http://documents.foodandwaterwatch.org/doc/CostofFoodMonopolies.pdf"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">http://documents.foodandwaterwatch.org/doc/CostofFoodMonopolies.pdf</span></a></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><a href="http://www.foodandwaterwatch.org/reports/biotech-ambassadors-eu/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.foodandwaterwatch.org/reports/biotech-ambassadors-eu/</span></a></p><h1 style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt; page-break-after:avoid; page-break-inside:avoid"><span style="color:#365f91; font-family:Cambria; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold">EU Version – Biotech Ambassadors: How the U.S. State Department Promotes the Seed Industry’s Global Agenda</span></h1><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><a href="http://www.foodandwaterwatch.org/research/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; text-decoration:underline">http://www.foodandwaterwatch.org/research/</span></a></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold">On Ronald Regan - random internet bits and pieces</span></p><p style="margin:1.4pt 0pt 0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-style:italic">“Reagan was, in the Stalinist sense, the greatest Marxist of the twentieth 